                    </div>
                    <span>When I started sailing my 27 foot sloop, I knew very little about sailing. I bought this book and used it to teach myself to sail. Now years later I still refer to it from time to time. I definitely think this is one of several books that all sailors should have on their bookshelves. I keep The Annapolis Book of Seamanship handy on my boat at all times.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Annapolis of Sailing</div>
