                    <span>I just finished a ton of sailing classes,starting w/the Laser & moving on to bigger and better, but NOT WITHOUT the help of this book!!YOU wanna SAIL?FOR REAL?BUY IT!READ IT!LEARN IT!LIVE IT!You can't lose...or drowned!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">If You Are A Sailor, You NEED This Book!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
